SIMPLE: im
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Im
<hw>I'm</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A contraction of <xex>I
am</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Im-</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Im-
<hw>Im-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A form of the prefix <xex>in-</xex> not,
and <xex>in-</xex> in. See <er>In-</er>. <xex>Im-</xex> also occurs in
composition with some words not of Latin origin; <as>as,
<ex>im</ex>bank, <ex>im</ex>bitter</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Image</ent>⟦br⟧
